   <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit">
    <property name="enabled">
     <bool>false</bool>
    </property>
    <property name="geometry">
     <rect>
      <x>110</x>
      <y>100</y>
      <width>421</width>
      <height>161</height>
     </rect>
    </property>
    <property name="styleSheet">
     <string notr="true"> QTextEdit {
        background: transparent;
	    font: 8pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        font-size: 10pt;
        border: none;
    }
</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;Though more revolutionary in tone, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;El Filibusterismo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;still stressed the importance of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;social reform&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; and the eradication of colonial corruption. Rizal did not call for outright &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;rebellion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; in the traditional sense, but rather sought a radical change in the structures of power in the Philippines—emphasizing that the Filipino people were capable of transforming their society.      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
    </property>
   </widget>
   <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit_2">
    <property name="enabled">
     <bool>false</bool>
    </property>
    <property name="geometry">
     <rect>
      <x>110</x>
      <y>250</y>
      <width>421</width>
      <height>471</height>
     </rect>
    </property>
    <property name="styleSheet">
     <string notr="true">
    QTextEdit {
        background: transparent;
        font: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        font-size: 10pt;
        border: none;
    }
</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; Contributions to Reformist Newspapers: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;La Solidaridad&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;In addition to his novels, Rizal was actively involved in journalism. He contributed essays and articles to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;La Solidaridad&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, a reformist newspaper founded by Filipino expatriates in Spain in the late 1880s. The newspaper became a platform for Filipinos advocating for reform, as well as a vehicle for promoting the ideas of equality, justice, and political representation.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;Rizal’s articles often challenged the Spanish authorities, highlighting the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;corruption&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; and abuses of the Spanish friars, and calling for reforms that would allow Filipinos to have a voice in the Philippine government. His writings in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;La Solidaridad&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; were crucial in spreading his advocacy for peaceful reform and nationalism among the Filipino intellectual class.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman';&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
    </property>
   </widget>
