    <property name="styleSheet">
     <string notr="true">
    QTextEdit {
        background: transparent;
        font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        font-size: 10pt;
        border: none;
    }
</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Return to the Philippines and the Foundation of La Liga Filipina (1892&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;docs-internal-guid-a1e5e7cd-7fff-82a8-9971-026ee8bc1386&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Arial,sans-serif'; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;I&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;n 1892, after spending a decade in Europe, Rizal returned to the Philippines, where his ideas for reform were more relevant than ever. Rizal’s return was part of his effort to organize a movement that would lead to peaceful reform and nation-building. Upon his return, he founded La Liga Filipina, a civic organization designed to unite Filipinos for the purpose of advocating for legal and social reforms. La Liga aimed to encourage the economic, educational, and political empowerment of Filipinos and to advocate for reforms such as the establishment of local government and equal rights for Filipinos under Spanish rule.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
    </property>
   </widget>
